ChaoticCard is a personal site application based on the ChaoticSoul theme for Wordpress. 
It's built using the micro-framework Silex, Doctrine, Twig as template engine, and uses a SQLite database. 

Example: <a href="http://samy.dindane.com/">http://samy.dindane.com/</a>

Features to come: 
- An admin page to edit the vCard 
- Themes support 
- Language selector
- Enhanced SEO
- Using javascript to display the mail addresses